N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 367.12 - General prohibition

State Regulations

All contracts or agreements entered into between or among
persons subject to this Part must be consistent with this Part and with title
10 of article 27 of the Environmental Conservation Law. No such contract or
agreement may be designed to hinder or frustrate the purpose or intent of this

Part. Notes
